OL,6,FCouncillor Sankey said: "It is
OL,7,Fheartbreaking, genuinely sickening, to
OL,8,Flook at the amount of money, the
OL,9,Fmillions spent on this reckless
OL,10,Fventure.
OL,12,F"It's not going into the pockets and
OL,13,Fthe futures of the people of this
OL,14,Fcity, the children, the families that
OL,15,Fare made homeless because we have so
OL,16,Fmuch pressure on the general fund.
OL,18,F"This money has been taken from the
OL,19,Fmouths and the pockets of the people
OL,20,Fof this city."
