OL,6,FThe council brokered the loan from the
OL,7,FPublic Works Loan Board ` and still
OL,8,Fowes #32 million or about #2.2 million
OL,9,Fa year over the next 16 years until
OL,10,F2041.
OL,12,FThe Labour deputy leader of the
OL,13,Fcouncil Jacob Taylor has been working
OL,14,Fwith the administrators to deal with
OL,15,Fthe "bad hand" the council has been
OL,16,Fdealt.
OL,18,FCouncillor Taylor said: "It was with
OL,19,Fno pleasure that any of us saw the
OL,20,Fattraction shut and 109 people made
OL,21,Fredundant at the end of last year.
